7923:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_tim.c ****   * @param  TIM_ICSelection specifies the input to be used.
7924:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_tim.c ****   *          This parameter can be one of the following values:
